add rule inet filter input iifname eth1 tcp dport 9152-9229 counter accept
add rule inet nat prerouting iifname eth1 ip daddr 10.152.152.10 tcp dport 9051 counter redirect to :9051
add rule inet nat prerouting iifname eth1 ip6 daddr fd19:c33d:88bc::10 tcp dport 9051 counter redirect to :9051
